WEBVTT

00:03:01.440 --> 00:03:04.240
He then just glances at our son and says,

00:03:06.120 --> 00:03:07.320
"He has it, too."

00:03:09.400 --> 00:03:14.240
We want to flee
back to the land of normal.

00:03:18.920 --> 00:03:20.336
Two days after Christmas,

00:03:20.360 --> 00:03:23.376
researchers come
from a university in Boston,

00:03:23.400 --> 00:03:25.896
and they take blood
from us and our children

00:03:25.920 --> 00:03:28.560
for a research project
focused on finding the gene.

00:03:29.360 --> 00:03:30.736
A few days later,